extendedInfo.description: Positive Thinking Power - the latest and best free positive thinking app on Google Play.Discover how you can tap into the power of your mind with positive thinking thats so powerful it will change your life today. Unleash a new force in your life that will make 2013 the best year you've ever had.Included in this app are pages of the powerful information you need, plus motivating videos and an unannounced bonus for more Brain Power than you thought you had.Learn how to think positively, change your surroundings, visualize and affirm daily, think calmly, control stress, exercise your brain, be more productive, stay active....the list goes on and on and it's all contained in this app, for you, for free!
